title: Stray Cats *LIVE* at Brixton Academy, UK.
description:
Brian and the boys reunite for this "Rumble in Brixton" LIVE show at the Brixton Academy in the UK some 25 years after their first concert there. If you are a fan of Rockabilly/50's style Rock-n-Roll/Hoochie Coochie, then this is the concert for you! Even being a "little" older doesn't stop these cats from Rockin' the house!

Playin' their hits and adding some new stuff to the list, some of the songs include "Rumble in Brixton", Please, Make up your Mind", "Rock this Town", "Stray Cats Strut", "Rock with Jim and Eddie (Beep Bop A Loola medley)", "Too Hip, Gotta Go", and more.
